Nursery Teacher
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 10:48:28
Ref. JB3045419
Job Description
We are a nursery based in Jumeirah seeking Early years teachers for September 2014.
An excellent opportunity awaits a western trained Early Years / Nursery Teacher in the Emirate of Dubai, UAE. The role will see you teach across the ages of 12mths – 4
years starting August / September 2014. This nursery is highly regarded in the Emirate for both local and western families. The role would suit a dedicated candidate who’s looking to immerse themselves in the Arabic culture. Further professional training is provided throughout the course of your contract. This excellent opportunity is holding immediate interviews for selected candidates. To be considered, submit your CV for immediate consideration. Supporting references are welcomed.
Skills
To be considered you must be tertiary qualified with either a Masters, Bachelor or PGCE / Diploma in Early Childhood or Primary Education from a native English speaking university. You must also have a minimum of two years experience working in an Early Years / Kindergarten.
Education
Early Childhood or Primary Education
